What is a server
A server is a software system that offers services, data and website info to the browser/client or the network on request

What is the role of the domain name
role of a domain name is used to translate or translate the IP address to its website name

What type of DNS record www is in www.foobar.com
Its's called the CNAME recod and the www past is a subdomain

What is the role of the web server
to provide quick information about a website and its content to the client on the web

What is the role of the application server
provides dynamic websites and information to the client

What is the role of the database
A databse is a system that stores valuable and vast information about basically anything

What is the server using to communicate with the computer of the user requesting the website
it uses HTTP or HTTPS
